        public IRoute getRoute()
        Get route by uri, you should get a route by this way and set some extras data before open
        返回:

        and it also will be IRoute.EmptyRoute if it not found

      • getBaseRoute

        public IBaseRoute getBaseRoute()

        Get IBaseRoute by uri, it could be one of IActivityRoute or IActionRoute. and you can add some Bundle data and RouteInterceptor into it.

        返回:
        returns an IBaseRoute finds by uri or IBaseRoute.EmptyBaseRoute for not found

      • getActivityRoute
